Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman's getting shipped?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's been decided that it'll be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom. What happened to Emma's leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it was a clean break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll heal back to normal without any scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably take a month or two\Nto completely heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's healed by your birthday, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to give me that bag later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let's go back to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman is getting shipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our rope was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma's leg is broken and she can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma's leg will heal quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can make more rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The escape will happen,\Nso we'll make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But first, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why? Why is Norman getting shipped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom was talking about the next shipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When she said the situation changed,\Nshe was talking about Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't believe even Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was her usual\Nenergetic self this morning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was smiling\Nand doing laundry, like normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now, she's no longer alive\Nanywhere in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. All she took was the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The plan isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your leg will heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's not it! We have to do something\Nabout your shipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The escape will succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You have to be with us, or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. I'll get you some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have him escape, obviously!\NNo matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don. Gilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to let Norman escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:07:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman, tomorrow afternoon,\Nescape by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be more precise, tomorrow afternoon,\Nmake it seem like you've escaped by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disable the tracking device,\Nand pretend to have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, hide in the area\Nuntil Emma's leg is healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And on the day we escape,\Nyou'll run away with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But even if it may not be true,\Nonce I run away, the security will get tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the House's caretaking policies,\Nsecurity won't increase much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caretaking policies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One, to let us grow freely and comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two, strict confidentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The first point is best\Nfor our developing brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A healthy child who grew up freely\Nwith rich emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the minimum obligation\Nfor the person in charge of the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that means point two is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The demons won't show themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they rule us with fear,\Nour brains won't develop into what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they do change the security, they would only\Nincrease the number of guards or caretakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's something we can deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they increase the height\Nof the wall to something we can't climb,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how will you climb over it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can make a ladder\Nwhile you're hiding or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if they change the tracking device\Nto a more complex one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they implant new ones, we'll know\Nwhere they are, so we can just take them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You get it, right? You don't have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll supply your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep you hidden no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can more or less deal with tighter security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a trump card to outwit Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend to run away, and with this method...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it. It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just about security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I run, you or Emma\Nmight get shipped out in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For one of you to get killed instead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't want that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They can have my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But I have no intention\Nof giving them anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll destroy what Mom has plotted\Nand make sure the escape succeeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should come up with and decide\Non a plan for after I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then what were the last six years of my life for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then Ray, you should break your leg, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, right? Yeah, let's break a bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, since I'm hurt so badly,\NI don't think I'll get shipped out in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what the demon at the gate said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're high-grade merchandise,\Nand we're also special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we go, we have to be in perfect form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if they need a replacement, it'd be Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if Ray were hurt badly as well,\Nhe wouldn't get shipped out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea.\NAll right, let's get cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't my arm be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. Then let's break your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. It's not guaranteed that\Nyou won't get shipped out if you get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then catch a horrible cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The demons won't eat me if I'm sick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking your arm is super painful and it'll be\Nexhausting to be sick, but you'll be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can discuss escape plans\Nthrough string telephones or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. We won't have to worry\Nabout Mom hearing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that doesn't work, we'll think\Nof something else. I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's way better than having you die, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all escape together, with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not part of this, I won't accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep living, together. Okay, Norman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use this to disable your tracking device\Ntomorrow, and then go hide in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then climb the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and inspect. Let's get it done\Nbefore they increase security.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don and Gilda\Nare making new rope right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're using spare sheets\Nstolen from the linen room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Press it against your left ear\Nand push the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That'll disable the tracking device.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With this method, it won't notify Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make that from camera parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not just the camera. I used parts\Nfrom all the other rewards I got beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted the strobe light from the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You spent six years getting parts from\Ndifferent items so Mom wouldn't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not amazing or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I realized the secret of the House,\NI had to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find out\Nabout the House's secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you about it before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because normally, no one would find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what infantile amnesia is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without being aware, people forget\Ntheir memories from when they were a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's infantile amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In rare cases,\Nit doesn't happen to some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have memories from when I was a fetus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There were inconsistencies between\Nmy own memories and my life at this House.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My first memory\Nis being inside a dark, warm liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A lullaby I could hear from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's in fragments, but highly detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I remember how the demons looked,\Nand that there were other babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tracking devices were implanted,\Nand we were divided into groups of five.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Groups of five...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I passed through a dark tunnel\Nand arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tunnel being the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. So past the gate isn't the outside, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The headquarters and the adjacent five plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes this House.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what Sister said was true, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The gate won't serve as an escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that is not just a few guards out there.\NIt's swarming with demons and adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's why the security towards us is light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll only focus on the gate\Nand won't increase security.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once Emma's leg is healed, we'll escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, you'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone. I have good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A foster family has been decided for Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is sudden,\Nbut he's leaving tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to miss him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congwats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play a lot tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We'll miss you.\N- Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Congratulations.\N- Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Congratulations, Norman!\N- Please don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman... congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please write us letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's kind of sad though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She's still crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's eat dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ba-baam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ba-ba-baam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- That felt good.\N- Hey, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Phew, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Norman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You bastard, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can still run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I want you to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Past the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is a cliff.
